<h2>Colors</h2>
<p>
    Animate <code>BackgroundColor</code>, <code>Color</code>, <code>BorderColor</code>, and other
    color properties using any valid CSS color format — hex, rgb(), rgba(), hsl(), or named colors.
    BlazorMotion interpolates channels smoothly in RGBA space.
</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Motion Animate="@@(new AnimationProps { BackgroundColor = "#6c47ff" })"
        Transition="@@(new TransitionConfig { Duration = 0.4 })" /&gt;

&lt;!-- Named colors --&gt;
&lt;Motion Animate="@@(new AnimationProps { Color = "tomato" })" /&gt;

&lt;!-- Color on hover --&gt;
&lt;Motion Animate="@@(new AnimationProps { BackgroundColor = "#1e1e2e" })"
        WhileHover="@@(new AnimationProps { BackgroundColor = "#6c47ff", Scale = 1.05 })"
        Transition="@@(new TransitionConfig { Duration = 0.2 })" /&gt;</code></pre>

<div class="demo-area" style="display:flex;gap:1.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;align-items:center;">
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">
